            <h1> Tooltip</h1>
          </div>
         <p>Tooltip is used to provide an explanation for specific items. E.g: icon action, text, image explantion...</p>
          <div class="bs-docs-example">
           <a data-placement="bottom" rel="tooltip" class="actionIcon" data-original-title="Edit">
               	<i class="uiIconViewUserInfo uiIconLightGray"></i>
              </a>
           
              <a data-placement="bottom" rel="tooltip" class="actionIcon" data-original-title="Delete">
               	<i class="uiIconDeleteUser uiIconLightGray"></i>
              </a>
          </div>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
&lt;a data-placement="bottom" rel="tooltip" class="actionIcon" data-original-title="Edit"&gt;
  &lt;i class="uiIconViewUserInfo uiIconLightGray"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;a data-placement="bottom" rel="tooltip" class="actionIcon" data-original-title="Delete"&gt;
  &lt;i class="uiIconDeleteUser uiIconLightGray"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;
</pre>
<div class="bs-docs-example">
The <a data-placement="bottom" rel="tooltip" data-toggle="tooltip" href="#" data-original-title="eXo Platform 4">PLF 4</a> includes Portal, <a data-placement="bottom" rel="tooltip" data-toggle="tooltip" href="#" data-original-title="Enterprise Content Management System">ECMS</a>,<a data-placement="bottom" rel="tooltip" title="" data-toggle="tooltip" href="#" data-original-title="Knowledge Suite"> KS</a>,<a data-placement="bottom" rel="tooltip" data-toggle="tooltip" href="#" data-original-title="Collaboration Suite"> CS</a>, and Social.
